  • Method Details

    • cancel

      boolean cancel()

      Attempts to cancel the execution of this task.

      If the task is already cancelled, or already executed, this method has no effect and returns false.

      Otherwise, the execution of this task is cancelled and this method returns true.

      Returns:
      whether the task was cancelled
